description: A cartoon image shows a woman with an animated appearance. The woman has a light skin tone, blond hair, and is wearing a green hair wrap on her head. She is also wearing a pink dress with white straps. The dress features a strawberry pattern. A light blue word "Done" appears in the upper left hand corner as she brushes dust off her hands. Her fingernails are painted a bright red. She has blue eyes and red lipstick. Her eyes slowly close.
